data.description: A rare find in Glendale. Two lots measuring 22.50 x 100 and 20 x 100 that must be sold together. Beautifully maintained single semi-detached home with amazing side yard. Gut renovated in the past. Lot has private driveway, two car garage, seating area, mature trees, and is completely fenced for ultimate privacy. Home has beautiful HW floors throughout. First floor has entry foyer, formal LR with Fireplace, which leads to formal DR, EIK and screened in back porch. Second floor has three bedrooms, plenty of closets and storage, and full bathroom. Basement has  LVT flooring, washer/dryer, utilities and OSE. SD # 24. New Anderson window recently installed.  Electric and plumbing are updated. Per sellers instructions, pre-approval or proof of funds required for all appointments.A MUST SEE!!
